{"title":"批量修改文件后缀名","num_read":312,"num_like":1019,"num_collection":604,"num_comments":242,"slug":"resource-system-Windows-renameFileSuffix","date":"2019-11-25T16:00:00.000Z","img":"/img/header_img/16.gif","_id":"clhrbp2ga00kko5lghpgdf4pj","site":{"data":{}},"updated":"2022-01-12T06:02:46.000Z","author":"Sunfy","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/resource-system-Windows-renameFileSuffix.json","webPath":"2019/11/26/resource-system-Windows-renameFileSuffix/","permalink":"https://sunfy9.gitee.io/2019/11/26/resource-system-Windows-renameFileSuffix/","excerpt":"各个系统下批量修改文件后缀名（Windows,Ubuntu,CentOS）","covers":null,"keywords":"sunfy, hexo-theme-snail","content":"<p>各个系统下批量修改文件后缀名（Windows,Ubuntu,CentOS） <a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"windows修改\"><a href=\"#windows修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"windows修改\"></a>windows修改</h3><ol>\n<li><p>在所需修改的文件目录下，新建txt文件．此处什么类型的文件都可以，主要就是新建一个文件，通过命令修改。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>打开新建的文件，填写</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ren *.png *.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li><p>说明：此处命令将当前文件所在目录下的png后缀修改为txt</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>将新建文件后缀名修改为bat，将文件放在要修改目录下双击即可完成。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"Ubuntu修改\"><a href=\"#Ubuntu修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Ubuntu修改\"></a>Ubuntu修改<sunfy-line></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 当前目录下的后缀名为.c的文件更改为.h的文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 格式  :</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 原字符串：将文件名需要替换的字符串；</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 目标字符串：将文件名中含有的原字符替换成目标字符串；</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 文件：指定要改变文件名的文件列表。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> rename <span class=\"string\">'命令参数/原串/替换后的串/'</span> 目录文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> s       表示替换</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">rename 's/\\.c/\\.h/'  ./*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"CentOS修改\"><a href=\"#CentOS修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CentOS修改\"></a>CentOS修改</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 把当前目录下的后缀名为.c的文件更改为.h的文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">rename .c .h *.c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Shell脚本解决\"><a href=\"#Shell脚本解决\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Shell脚本解决\"></a>Shell脚本解决</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\">!/bin/bash</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">find ./ -name *.c | while read i</span><br><span class=\"line\">do</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo \"$i\";</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mv $i.c $i.h</span><br><span class=\"line\">done</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"find-xargs-解决\"><a href=\"#find-xargs-解决\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"find xargs 解决\"></a>find xargs 解决</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 递归的更改，会更改当前目录下及其子目录下所有匹配文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">find ./ -name \"*.c\" | awk -F \".\" '&#123;print $2&#125;' | xargs -i -t mv ./&#123;&#125;.c ./&#123;&#125;.h</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","more":"</p>\n<h3 id=\"windows修改\"><a href=\"#windows修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"windows修改\"></a>windows修改</h3><ol>\n<li><p>在所需修改的文件目录下，新建txt文件．此处什么类型的文件都可以，主要就是新建一个文件，通过命令修改。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>打开新建的文件，填写</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ren *.png *.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ol>\n<li><p>说明：此处命令将当前文件所在目录下的png后缀修改为txt</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>将新建文件后缀名修改为bat，将文件放在要修改目录下双击即可完成。</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"Ubuntu修改\"><a href=\"#Ubuntu修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Ubuntu修改\"></a>Ubuntu修改<sunfy-line></h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 当前目录下的后缀名为.c的文件更改为.h的文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 格式  :</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 原字符串：将文件名需要替换的字符串；</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 目标字符串：将文件名中含有的原字符替换成目标字符串；</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 文件：指定要改变文件名的文件列表。</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> rename <span class=\"string\">'命令参数/原串/替换后的串/'</span> 目录文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> s       表示替换</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">rename 's/\\.c/\\.h/'  ./*</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"CentOS修改\"><a href=\"#CentOS修改\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CentOS修改\"></a>CentOS修改</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 把当前目录下的后缀名为.c的文件更改为.h的文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">rename .c .h *.c</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"Shell脚本解决\"><a href=\"#Shell脚本解决\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Shell脚本解决\"></a>Shell脚本解决</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\">!/bin/bash</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">find ./ -name *.c | while read i</span><br><span class=\"line\">do</span><br><span class=\"line\">    echo \"$i\";</span><br><span class=\"line\">    mv $i.c $i.h</span><br><span class=\"line\">done</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"find-xargs-解决\"><a href=\"#find-xargs-解决\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"find xargs 解决\"></a>find xargs 解决</h3><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> 递归的更改，会更改当前目录下及其子目录下所有匹配文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">find ./ -name \"*.c\" | awk -F \".\" '&#123;print $2&#125;' | xargs -i -t mv ./&#123;&#125;.c ./&#123;&#125;.h</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","next":{"title":"Redis集群搭建","path":"api/articles/resource-java-redis-redisCluster.json","image":"/img/header_img/java/redis-sentinel.jpg","num_read":394,"num_like":129,"num_collection":838,"num_comments":35},"prev":{"title":"高并发Redis缓存那些事儿","path":"api/articles/resource-java-redis-redisCache.json","image":"/img/header_img/java/redisCaches.png","num_read":637,"num_like":181,"num_collection":314,"num_comments":40},"categories":[{"name":"工具集","path":"api/categories/工具集.json","pathContent":"api/categories/工具集","description":"各种工具类相关","cover":"https://sunfy9.gitee.io/img/header_img/sunfy-default.png"}],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","path":"api/tags/Linux.json","pathContent":"api/tags/Linux","description":"全称GNU/Linux，是一种免费使用和自由传播的类UNIX操作系统","cover":"https://sunfy9.gitee.io/project/photo/project/linux.jpg"},{"name":"windows","path":"api/tags/windows.json","pathContent":"api/tags/windows","description":"[windows]暂未设置说明","cover":"https://sunfy9.gitee.io/img/header_img/sunfy-default.png"}]}